Functions necessary


 - create a scroll       Inventory -> Menu -> New
 - rename a scroll      Inventory -> Menu -> Scrolls -> [> Edit]
 - delete a scroll      Inventory -> Menu -> Scrolls -> [> Delete]
 - list scrolls         Inventory -> Menu -> Scrolls

 - open a scroll       Inventory -> Menu -> Scrolls -> [> Open]

 - add an item         Inventory -> Add Item
 - edit an item        Inventory -> [Edit]
 - delete an item      Inventory -> [Delete]

 - move an item?      N/A
 - check an item?     N/A

 Create a scroll: Inventory -> +
 Rename a scroll: Inventory -> DblClick
 Delete a scroll: Inventory -> List -> [Close]
 List scrolls: Inventory -> List

 Open a scroll: Inventory -> List -> Click

 Add an item:   Inventory -> +Item
 Edit an item: Inventory + [DblClick]
 Delete an item: Inventory + [X]

 Move an item: Inventory + Select + Up/Down
 Check of an item: Inventory + Select + Tick


